<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">About</h1>

<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
  <p class="mb-4">Welcome to our event management platform! Our application is designed to streamline the management of events, attendees, and event types. Here is a brief overview of our key components:</p>

  <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Key Components:</h2>

  <ul class="mb-4">
    <li class="mb-2">
      <strong>Events Table:</strong> Stores details of each event, including its unique identifier (id), name, date, location, description, and event type (linked via event_type_id to EventTypes table).
    </li>
    <li class="mb-2">
      <strong>EventTypes Table:</strong> Contains predefined types of events with their unique identifiers (id) and names. Each event belongs to exactly one event type.
    </li>
    <li class="mb-2">
      <strong>Attendees Table:</strong> Holds information about attendees, including their unique identifier (id), name, email, and attendance status.
    </li>
    <li class="mb-2">
      <strong>AttendeesEvents Table (Join Table):</strong> Facilitates the many-to-many relationship between events and attendees. It stores pairs of attendee_id and event_id to associate attendees with specific events.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mb-4">Our platform aims to provide seamless management and coordination of events, ensuring efficient handling of attendee registrations and event types for a smooth user experience.</p>
</div>


